Text:
It’s gameday, Ohio!

Excited to watch the Bearcats take on the Crimson Tide this afternoon!

@GoBearcatsFB @CFBPlayoff #CinCityPride https://t.co/byDP694buS

Looking forward to speaking at the #AHIS2021 Advanced Healthcare Innovation Summit this morning around 10am. 

Will discuss our legislative response to COVID, my decision to participate in the J&amp;J trial and more on health care! Make sure to tune in. 
@Innovativehci

Decades of neglect has left America’s infrastructure in a state of disrepair.

@ASCETweets gives our infrastructure a “C-”.

Thankfully, with the Infrastructure Investment &amp; Jobs Act, relief is finally on the way. Let’s get this bill through the House &amp; to @POTUS’ desk w/o delay.
